---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Accessibility Statement" description="Accessibility statement for Lonell's Soul Food Cuisine — our commitment to digital accessibility.">
  <div class="min-h-screen pb-16">
    <Section eyebrow="Legal" title="Accessibility Statement" description="Last updated: June 2026">
      <div class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p>
          Lonell's Soul Food Cuisine is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for all visitors,
          including those with disabilities. We strive to provide a website experience that is accessible
          to the widest possible audience, regardless of technology or ability.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8 mb-3">Our Efforts</h3>
        <p>We aim to comply with the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA standards. Our ongoing accessibility efforts include:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Semantic HTML structure for screen reader compatibility</li>
          <li>ARIA labels on interactive elements</li>
          <li>Keyboard-navigable menus and forms</li>
          <li>High-contrast color schemes meeting WCAG AA requirements</li>
          <li>Descriptive alt text on all images</li>
          <li>Skip-to-content navigation links</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8 mb-3">Feedback</h3>
        <p>
          We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of our website. If you encounter any barriers or
          have suggestions for improvement, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+13234513104" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">(323) 451-3104</a></li>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:reservations@lonells.com" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">reservations@lonells.com</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-8 mb-3">Ongoing Improvement</h3>
        <p>
          Accessibility is an ongoing effort. We regularly review our website to identify and fix
          accessibility issues, and we are committed to providing a seamless experience for all visitors.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
